{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. HOTEL ROOM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A standard room looking out at the water which is dotted with sailboats and cruise ships.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bed is covered with hi- tech surveillance equipment.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The equipment salesman, LONNIE, 40's, who makes a fetish of gadgetry, explains the finer points of operation to FRANCISCO "FRANKIE" FLORES, 30's, sallow, watery-eyed, in expensive clothes.
