{DIALOGUE}: Because the technology to intrude has reached the masses.
{DIALOGUE}: Your competitor, your ex-spouse, adversaries, stalkers, they're at the local electronics store right now, and they're gonna be intruding on you not only through your telephone, but your fax, cell phone, pager, cable TV, Musak, windows, walls, air conditioning ventilation, modem, and internet connection.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He walks over to the bed and the sexy equipment --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LONNIE
{DIALOGUE}: Nobody has these babies, no way, not the shiznit.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Frederico picks up a piece of equipment.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRANCISCO
