{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Javier finishes his beer, rises, and takes the empty seat next to Francisco.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Manolo watches.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Very quickly Javi strikes up a conversation.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We don't hear what they're saying but it doesn't matter because Francisco clearly likes Javi.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Off Francisco's anticipatory smile --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OMITTED
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OMITTED
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. MILITARY BASE - MEXICO - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The back of a blue van opens and a blindfolded Francisco falls onto the ground.
