{DIALOGUE}: I snuck out --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CAROLINE
{DIALOGUE}: Are you kidding... I'm staying with you --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SETH
{DIALOGUE}: He's gonna fucking die right here on the kitchen floor --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANOTHER KID
{DIALOGUE}: He can't.
{DIALOGUE}: My parents are in Barbados --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OMITTED
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. SUBURBAN HOSPITAL EMERGENCY ENTRANCE - NIGHT
