{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OMITTED
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. TORTURE ROOM - BARRACKS - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Francisco is strapped naked into a chair.
