{CHARACTER_NAME}: ROBERT
{DIALOGUE}: How long have you known about this?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: No response.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ROBERT
{META_DATA}: (yelling)
{DIALOGUE}: How long have you known?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BARBARA
{DIALOGUE}: Six months.
{DIALOGUE}: I found some marijuana, that's all.
