{META_DATA}: (he blinks)
{DIALOGUE}: That you don't have time for.
{DIALOGUE}: I suggest you look into the Coronel...
{META_DATA}: (he blinks again)
{DIALOGUE}: Into selling it.
{DIALOGUE}: If you can stomach it, you should look into it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: That painting is very valuable.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HELENA
{DIALOGUE}: I don't understand.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CARLOS
