{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sheila is reluctant to answer.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SHEILA
{DIALOGUE}: No, not really.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Helena catches Carl's eye and they share a grim moment.
