{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: All around them a GROUP of 3rd graders, in identical T-shirts, enjoy a field trip.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRANCISCO (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: I love this place.
{DIALOGUE}: Don't turn around.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Behind her Francisco Flores takes a photo with an instant camera.
