{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. WEST END STREETS - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Robert drives through the streets in his Cadillac DeVille.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. DEVILLE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Robert rides in glum silence.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He looks at passersby who are almost all black and almost all stare back at the white man in his Cadillac.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A group of young men stare threateningly as he rolls past.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: On the street, in the lee of a Brownstone staircase, a deal is going down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ROBERT AND SETH ABRAHMS - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: sit in a coffee shop.
