{DIALOGUE}: I'm surprised she hasn't called.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANOTHER ANGLE ON ROBERT IN THE CAR - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He turns a corner and is suddenly in a drive-thru drug market.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dealers, HUSTLERS, run at the windows from both sides, signaling.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HUSTLERS
{DIALOGUE}: What you want?
{DIALOGUE}: Rock?
{DIALOGUE}: Rock?
{DIALOGUE}: Hey, what you want?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ROBERT AND SETH - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: in the coffee shop.
