{DIALOGUE}: We sometimes went downtown to score.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ROBERT
{DIALOGUE}: What?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SETH
{DIALOGUE}: The West End.
{DIALOGUE}: We buy it off the streets.
{META_DATA}: (beat)
