{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, like turning into a beautiful woman.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They reach the car.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RUIZ
{DIALOGUE}: Would you mind if today we walked?
{DIALOGUE}: It's one block.
{DIALOGUE}: I could use the fresh air.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OMITTED
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. FRANCISCO'S CAR - CONTINUOUS
